import React from 'react' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' function OwnerHomepage({currentOwner, setCurrentOwner}) { const [ownerData, setOwnerData] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { fetch('/owner-homepage') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setOwnerData(data) }) }, []) return (

Welcome, {ownerData.name}

{ownerData.username}

Location: {ownerData.location}

Member since: {ownerData.date_joined}

Camera Equipment: {ownerData.camera}

Editing Software: {ownerData.editing}

Light Kit: {ownerData.lights}

Audio Equipment: {ownerData.audio}

Props: {ownerData.props}

Bio: {ownerData.bio}

) } export default OwnerHomepage
